<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3428899">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Tue, 04/09/2013 - 19:22 | <a href="/news/2013-04-09/guest-post-bitcoin-money-future-or-old-fashioned-bubble#comment-3428899" class="active">3428899</a></span>
